      "name": "Construct stiffness QoI comparison — FEA vs. experiment",
      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness was compared against the mean experimental stiffness from N=11 bench tests (Lab 1: n=6, Lab 2: n=5). The ensemble mean FEA prediction fell within 4.2% of the pooled experimental mean (experimental: 187.3 ± 12.1 N/mm; FEA ensemble mean: 195.2 N/mm). The normalised error metric E/uval = 0.81, well below the acceptance threshold of 1.96. Acceptance criterion satisfied.",
